<module status="bronze">
    <h>gabh</h>
    <p><g>gabh</g>
        <en>take</en> is a <a href="?xx=verbs/simple_verbs">simple verb</a>.</p>

    <section id="forms">
        <h>forms</h>
        <p>The principal parts of <g>gabh</g> are – <ul>
                <li><m>gabhaidh</m> – future independent, i.e. <en>will take</en></li>
                <li><m>ghabh</m> – past independent, i.e. <en>took</en></li>
                <li><m>gabhail</m> – verbal noun, i.e. <en>taking</en></li>
            </ul>
        </p>
        <section>
            <h>tense</h>
            <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>past <ul id="past">
                            <li>active <ul>
                                    <li>independent – <m>ghabh</m></li>
                                    <li>relative – a <m>ghabh</m></li>
                                    <li>dependent – cha/an/nach <m>do ghabh</m></li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                            <li>passive <ul>
                                    <li>independent – <m>ghabhadh</m></li>
                                    <li>relative – a <m>ghabhadh</m></li>
                                    <li>dependent – cha/an/nach <m>do ghabhadh</m></li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li>future <ul id="future">
                            <li>active <ul>
                                    <li>independent – <m>gabhaidh</m></li>
                                    <li>relative – a <m>ghabhas</m></li>
                                    <li>dependent – cha <m>ghabh</m>, an/nach <m>gabh</m></li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                            <li>passive <ul>
                                    <li>independent – <m>gabhar</m></li>
                                    <li>relative – a <m>ghabhar</m></li>
                                    <li>dependent – cha <m>ghabhar</m>, an/nach <m>gabhar</m></li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li>conditional <ul id="conditional">
                            <li>active <ul>
                                    <li>first person singular <ul>
                                            <li>independent – <m>ghabhainn</m></li>
                                            <li>relative – a <m>ghabhainn</m></li>
                                            <li>dependent – cha <m>ghabhainn</m>, an/nach
                                                  <m>gabhainn</m></li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </li>
                                    <li>first person plural <ul>
                                            <li>independent – <m>ghabhamaid</m></li>
                                            <li>relative – a <m>ghabhamaid</m></li>
                                            <li>dependent – cha <m>ghabhamaid</m>, an/nach
                                                  <m>gabhamaid</m></li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </li>
                                    <li>second/third persons <ul>
                                            <li>independent – <m>ghabhadh</m></li>
                                            <li>relative – a <m>ghabhadh</m></li>
                                            <li>dependent – cha <m>ghabhadh</m>, an/nach
                                                  <m>gabhadh</m></li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                            <li>passive <ul>
                                    <li>independent – <m>ghabhte</m></li>
                                    <li>relative – a <m>ghabhte</m></li>
                                    <li>dependent – cha <m>ghabhte</m>, an/nach <m>gabhte</m></li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h>status</h>
            <p><ul>
                    <li>independent <ul id="independent">
                            <li>past <ul>
                                    <li>active – <m>ghabh</m></li>
