        </section>
        <section>
            <h>imperative</h>
            <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>independent <ul id="imp-ind">
                            <li>first person singular – <m>gabham</m>!</li>
                            <li>second person singular – <m>gabh</m>!</li>
                            <li>first person plural – <m>gabhamaid</m>!</li>
                            <li>second person plural – <m>gabhaibh</m>!</li>
                            <li>third person – <m>gabhadh</m>!</li>
